title: Ganz-MÁVAG SE
text:
Ganz-MÁVAG Sport Egyesület was a <a href="Hungary">Hungarian</a> <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club from the town of <a href="Budapest">Budapest</a>, <a href="Hungary">Hungary</a>.
History.
Ganz-MÁVAG Sport Egyesület debuted in the <a href="1945%20Nemzeti%20Bajnoks%C3%A1g%20I">1945</a> season of the <a href="Hungarian%20League">Hungarian League</a> and finished eleventh.
